com.emmes.aps.medication

Class DBMedicationInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.emmes.aps.medication.DBMedicationInfo

  • public class DBMedicationInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class DBMedicationInfo is for handling the list item detail info. The medication is dislayed in a list by the listactivity MedicationListActivity. The list item is the object of type DBMedicationInfo.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Mahbubur Rahman
